charToIndices - Variable in class SequenceMatcher
For each distinct character x in b, charToIndices.get(x) is a list of the indices (into b) at which x appears, so if b2j.get('a') = [2, 4], b.charAt(2).equals(b.charAt(4) && b.charAt(2).equals('a')
